demo_mozrepl_perl version 0.01
=======================

This is a short demo of what the mozrepl plugin for Firefox can do and
how to use it from Perl to perform automated Quality Assurance.

INSTALLATION

    # cpanm Mojolicious::Lite
    # cpanm Mojolicious::Plugin::Bootstrap3

RUNNING

    $ morbo ./barcelona
    $ perl Makefile.PL
    $ make test

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    * Mojolicious::Lite
    * Mojolicious::Plugin::Bootstrap3


